# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:12
translate spanish suzy0_b52dca5a:

    # "I go to the kitchen and make a plate with what's left, then sit down across from her at the table."
    "Voy a la cocina y me preparo un plato con lo que queda, luego me siento frente a ella en la mesa."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:13
translate spanish suzy0_a9d96a39:

    # "She doesn't even look up at me as she casually eats, not really even paying attention to the fact that I'm there."
    "Ni siquiera me mira mientras come con naturalidad, sin prestar realmente atención al hecho de que estoy ahí."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:16
translate spanish breakfastmenu_752743ef:

    # pc "So how have you been doing?"
    pc "¿Qué tal te va?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:18
translate spanish breakfastmenu_7a0e54f8:

    # "She raises her eyes towards me, looking slightly annoyed by my question."
    "Levanta la vista hacia mí, con aire ligeramente molesto por mi pregunta."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:19
translate spanish breakfastmenu_19dcc455:

    # ss "I've been fine."
    ss "Estoy bien."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:20
translate spanish breakfastmenu_ed75df6c:

    # pc "School going okay?"
    pc "¿Te va bien en la escuela?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:21
translate spanish breakfastmenu_95991dd2:

    # ss "We've barely started the semester. I don't know how it's going."
    ss "Apenas hemos empezado el semestre. No sé cómo va."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:22
translate spanish breakfastmenu_6150338d:

    # pc "And work? You work at Java Lava, right?"
    pc "¿Y el trabajo? Trabajas en Java Lava, ¿verdad?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:24
translate spanish breakfastmenu_13de2504:

    # "She turns her phone off and slides it into her pocket, then really looks up at me for the first time."
    "Apaga el móvil y se lo guarda en el bolsillo, y entonces me mira de verdad por primera vez."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:25
translate spanish breakfastmenu_ae5be968:

    # ss "Yeah. It's fine. It's not too hard and I get paid."
    ss "Sí. Va bien. No es muy duro y me pagan."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:29
translate spanish breakfastmenu_e05d2344:

    # ss "Oh man, you wouldn't believe the guys we get in there."
    ss "Vaya, no te creerías el tipo de gente que viene por aquí."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:30
translate spanish breakfastmenu_322cf28b:

    # pc "Who's your weirdest."
    pc "¿Quién es el más raro?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:31
translate spanish breakfastmenu_cd997a04:

    # ss "So there was this one guy who comes in all the time. I don't even remember his name; we just call him kombucha guy."
    ss "Bueno, hay un tipo que viene todo el tiempo. Ni siquiera recuerdo su nombre; lo llamamos «el chico de la kombucha»."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:32
translate spanish breakfastmenu_be9a8d1f:

    # ss "We serve kombucha tea there, but it rarely gets ordered. But this guy comes in almost every day, at least four times a week, and buys two kombucha teas."
    ss "Allí servimos té de kombucha, pero casi nunca lo piden. Pero este tipo viene casi todos los días, al menos cuatro veces a la semana, y compra dos tés de kombucha."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:33
translate spanish breakfastmenu_23ceb711:

    # ss "He sits at a table by himself and stares out the window and drinks both of those teas back to back, then leaves a two-dollar tip and leaves."
    ss "Se sienta solo en una mesa, se queda mirando por la ventana y se bebe los dos tés seguidos, luego deja una propina de dos dólares y se va."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:34
translate spanish breakfastmenu_f53e358e:

    # pc "Weird. Have you ever talked to him?"
    pc "Qué raro. ¿Alguna vez has hablado con él?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:35
translate spanish breakfastmenu_0ef624f4:

    # ss "Oh yeah. He's a little crazy. He says that he's some kind of musician and he tried to get Tammy to go out with him. He told her that he's really famous over in Japan."
    ss "Ah, sí. Está un poco loco. Dice que es una especie de músico e intentó que Tammy saliera con él. Le dijo que es muy famoso en Japón."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:36
translate spanish breakfastmenu_d22ad849:

    # ss "Then he went on and on about how Japan is way better than here. How they have holographic baristas that make your coffee and bring it to your table."
    ss "Luego no paraba de hablar de que Japón es mucho mejor que aquí. De que tienen baristas holográficos que te preparan el café y te lo traen a la mesa."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:37
translate spanish breakfastmenu_fa3e4e10:

    # ss "How he bought a phone there five years ago for $20 and doesn't have to pay a monthly fee because it runs off a satellite."
    ss "Que compró allí un teléfono hace cinco años por 20 dólares y no tiene que pagar cuota mensual porque funciona por satélite."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:38
translate spanish breakfastmenu_ce59dba2:

    # pc "Wow."
    pc "Vaya."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:39
translate spanish breakfastmenu_faaa2ecb:

    # ss "He's always hitting on Tammy every time he comes in. She likes to mess with him too."
    ss "Siempre está coqueteando con Tammy cada vez que viene. A ella también le gusta tomárselo a broma."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:40
translate spanish breakfastmenu_9e19cf64:

    # ss "He came in one time and was telling her about how he invented this new clock that was small, and you could carry it around with you."
    ss "Una vez vino y le estaba contando que había inventado un reloj nuevo que era pequeño y que te lo podías llevar contigo."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:41
translate spanish breakfastmenu_5d1c5ae8:

    # pc "Isn't that just a watch?"
    pc "¿No es eso simplemente un reloj?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:42
translate spanish breakfastmenu_c152b77b:

    # ss "That's what Tammy said. He argued with her and told her it was completely different."
    ss "Eso es lo que dijo Tammy. Él discutió con ella y le dijo que era completamente diferente."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:43
translate spanish breakfastmenu_3791927f:

    # ss "So the next day she told him about how she had invented this new type of pastries that had fruit filling and were sold in individual packages and would fit perfectly in your toaster."
    ss "Así que al día siguiente ella le contó que había inventado un nuevo tipo de bollería con relleno de fruta, que se vendía en paquetes individuales y que cabía perfectamente en la tostadora."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:44
translate spanish breakfastmenu_74618d28:

    # pc "Pop Tarts?"
    pc "¿Pop Tarts?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:45
translate spanish breakfastmenu_c72adb9b:

    # ss "Yeah, but he'd apparently never heard of them, because he went on and on about how it was an amazing idea and how he wanted to pay her to buy that idea from her so he could make it."
    ss "Sí, pero al parecer él nunca había oído hablar de ellas, porque no paraba de decir que era una idea increíble y que quería pagarle para comprarle esa idea y poder fabricarlas."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:46
translate spanish breakfastmenu_e8b6bb21:

    # pc "Did she take his money?"
    pc "¿Le aceptó el dinero?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:47
translate spanish breakfastmenu_75e09394:

    # ss "Fifty bucks."
    ss "Cincuenta dólares."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:48
translate spanish breakfastmenu_5cbde015:

    # pc "That's fucked up!"
    pc "¡Qué locura!"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:50
translate spanish breakfastmenu_5f99478a:

    # ss "I know right?"
    ss "¿A que sí?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:51
translate spanish breakfastmenu_c085fd14:

    # "She starts laughing, and I can't help but to laugh too."
    "Ella se echa a reír, y yo no puedo evitar reírme también."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:55
translate spanish breakfastmenu_74c7877c:

    # ss "Yeah, I don't do that stuff. I kind of feel bad for him."
    ss "Sí, yo no hago esas cosas. Me da un poco de pena."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:56
translate spanish breakfastmenu_d31a7dfa:

    # ss "He seems like he's not playing with a full deck, you know? I figure he's probably had a rough life."
    ss "Parece que no está en sus cabales, ¿sabes? Supongo que probablemente ha tenido una vida dura."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:57
translate spanish breakfastmenu_9ccec7b2:

    # ss "But Tammy is just like that."
    ss "Pero Tammy es así."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:58
translate spanish breakfastmenu_e0586b57:

    # ss "She can take care of herself though. She does MMA, you know? Fights in a ring and everything."
    ss "Aunque sabe defenderse sola. Practica MMA, ¿sabes? Pelea en el ring y todo eso."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:59
translate spanish breakfastmenu_399bdc0f:

    # pc "Really?"
    pc "¿En serio?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:60
translate spanish breakfastmenu_02b90fe6:

    # ss "Yeah. She's good too. I've gone and watched her fight before. She can seriously kick some ass."
    ss "Sí. Ella también es buena. He ido a verla pelear antes. De verdad que sabe dar una buena paliza."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:61
translate spanish breakfastmenu_1189f258:

    # pc "You never wanted to get into it though?"
    pc "¿Pero nunca te ha apetecido probarlo?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:62
translate spanish breakfastmenu_a7e15ac4:

    # ss "Nah. It's too much work for me, and I really don't want to get hit."
    ss "No. Es demasiado trabajo para mí, y la verdad es que no quiero que me den."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:65
translate spanish breakfastmenu_9f26e184:

    # ss "Aw, thanks, [bro]. I'm glad you don't want me to get beat up."
    ss "Ay, gracias, [bro]. Me alegro de que no quieras que me den una paliza."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:66
translate spanish breakfastmenu_3090c620:

    # pc "If I saw somebody hitting you, even in a ring, even if it was a girl, I'd have to kick their ass. It's in the big [brother] rulebook."
    pc "Si viera a alguien pegándote, aunque fuera en un ring, aunque fuera una chica, tendría que darle una paliza. Está en el gran [brother] libro de reglas."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:68
translate spanish breakfastmenu_caad0343:

    # "She burst into laughter."
    "Ella se echó a reír."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:69
translate spanish breakfastmenu_0cfa18a1:

    # ss "I don't think you could even take these girls. Tammy would wipe the floor with you."
    ss "No creo que pudieras con estas chicas. Tammy te dejaría por los suelos."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:70
translate spanish breakfastmenu_ae871f39:

    # pc "Oh yeah?"
    pc "¿Ah, sí?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:72
translate spanish breakfastmenu_4122a41e:

    # ss "Yeah, definitely."
    ss "Sí, sin duda."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:73
translate spanish breakfastmenu_2d87f285:

    # pc "Well I'd get my ass kicked so you didn't have to then."
    pc "Bueno, entonces me darían una paliza a mí para que tú no tuvieras que recibirla."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:74
translate spanish breakfastmenu_906493b5:

    # ss "Really? You'd get your ass kicked for me?"
    ss "¿En serio? ¿Te darían una paliza por mí?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:77
translate spanish breakfastmenu_d120684f:

    # ss "I don't believe you."
    ss "No te creo."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:79
translate spanish breakfastmenu_9f7e6e8a:

    # ss "See, I knew it!"
    ss "¡Ves, lo sabía!"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:82
translate spanish breakfastmenu_934dd153:

    # ss "Anger? What anger? I'm not angry at anybody."
    ss "¿Ira? ¿Qué ira? No estoy enfadado con nadie."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:83
translate spanish breakfastmenu_b287d4be:

    # pc "You seem angry at me."
    pc "Pareces enfadado conmigo."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:84
translate spanish breakfastmenu_87014878:

    # ss "Well, if you were in the ring with me, yeah, I could channel that anger into an ass kicking."
    ss "Bueno, si estuvieras en el ring conmigo, sí, podría canalizar esa ira en una paliza."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:85
translate spanish breakfastmenu_e7037ffa:

    # pc "I don't know. I think I could take you."
    pc "No sé. Creo que podría ganarte."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:87
translate spanish breakfastmenu_a43ee1a8:

    # ss "Not as often as they do Tammy, but I get one or two a day."
    ss "No tan a menudo como a Tammy, pero me tocan uno o dos al día."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:88
translate spanish breakfastmenu_046a9753:

    # ss "I've gone on dates with a few of the guys that I've met there, but nothing really panned out."
    ss "He salido con algunos de los chicos que he conocido allí, pero nada ha salido bien."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:89
translate spanish breakfastmenu_b102ceb1:

    # pc "Nobody harassing you though?"
    pc "¿Pero nadie te acosa?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:90
translate spanish breakfastmenu_f72e097b:

    # ss "Nah, not really."
    ss "No, la verdad es que no."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:91
translate spanish breakfastmenu_0ac94505:

    # pc "Good. I'd hate to have to bust some heads."
    pc "Bien. No me gustaría tener que partirle la cara a nadie."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:93
translate spanish breakfastmenu_35df88eb:

    # ss "Bust heads? You? Don't make me laugh."
    ss "¿Partirle la cara? ¿Tú? No me hagas reír."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:94
translate spanish breakfastmenu_4d303faa:

    # pc "Hey! I could do it."
    pc "¡Oye! Podría hacerlo."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:98
translate spanish breakfastmenu_a79bfefa:

    # ss "Really? You're going to ask me how much I make. That's none of your damn business."
    ss "¿En serio? Vas a preguntarme cuánto gano. Eso no es de tu maldita cuenta."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:99
translate spanish breakfastmenu_02a4aa53:

    # pc "Sorry, I was just making conversation."
    pc "Lo siento, solo estaba entablando conversación."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:101
translate spanish breakfastmenu_e2bc9fa0:

    # ss "Well, make it with somebody else. I'm not interested in talking to you."
    ss "Bueno, entábla la con otra persona. No me interesa hablar contigo."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:102
translate spanish breakfastmenu_b57d2eab:

    # "Before I can apologize, she stands up and walks out of the room."
    "Antes de que pueda disculparme, se levanta y sale de la habitación."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:103
translate spanish breakfastmenu_d8f00519:

    # "I guess I'll have to try to fix things with her some other day."
    "Supongo que tendré que intentar arreglar las cosas con ella otro día."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:104
translate spanish breakfastmenu_c0aeac6d:

    # "I finish eating by myself and then clean off the table and get ready to go to school."
    "Termino de comer solo, luego recojo la mesa y me preparo para ir al colegio."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:108
translate spanish breakfastmenu_1b55d4a6:

    # ss "That doesn't really surprise me. You would suck at it."
    ss "Eso no me sorprende. Serías un desastre en eso."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:109
translate spanish breakfastmenu_142311fd:

    # ss "You're not good at talking to people. You just whine and get on everybody's nerves."
    ss "No se te da bien hablar con la gente. Solo te quejas y caes mal a todo el mundo."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:112
translate spanish breakfastmenu_d1097009:

    # ss "I think you whine too much and pity yourself, yes."
    ss "Creo que te quejas demasiado y te compadeces de ti mismo, sí."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:113
translate spanish breakfastmenu_a8b0992c:

    # pc "I'm really not like that though. You don't really even know me."
    pc "Pero en realidad no soy así. Ni siquiera me conoces."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:115
translate spanish breakfastmenu_952b2153:

    # ss "Sure you are. You whine and you pity yourself."
    ss "Claro que sí. Te quejas y te compadeces de ti mismo."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:116
translate spanish breakfastmenu_fbb5736d:

    # pc "You don't really even know me."
    pc "Ni siquiera me conoces de verdad."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:118
translate spanish breakfastmenu_db9ad157:

    # ss "Better than you. All you do is whine and pity yourself."
    ss "Mejor que tú. Lo único que haces es quejarte y compadecerte de ti mismo."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:119
translate spanish breakfastmenu_c4de7a83:

    # pc "What are you talking about. You barely even know me."
    pc "¿De qué estás hablando? Apenas me conoces."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:120
translate spanish breakfastmenu_9965969f:

    # ss "You never gave me the chance to get to know you. When we started getting used to each other and getting along, you just up and left."
    ss "Nunca me diste la oportunidad de conocerte. Cuando empezábamos a acostumbrarnos el uno al otro y a llevarnos bien, simplemente te levantaste y te fuiste."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:121
translate spanish breakfastmenu_9ef2ee78:

    # pc "I'm not going to leave this time. I'm going to stay here and help out."
    pc "Esta vez no me voy a ir. Me voy a quedar aquí y te voy a echar una mano."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:124
translate spanish breakfastmenu_c0dc7bfc:

    # ss "I don't see how that's any of your business, but yes. His name is Tim and he lives in Whiterock."
    ss "No veo por qué te incumbe eso, pero sí. Se llama Tim y vive en Whiterock."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:125
translate spanish breakfastmenu_130cbb47:

    # pc "How's the long-distance thing working out?"
    pc "¿Cómo va lo de la relación a distancia?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:127
translate spanish breakfastmenu_2c9e2c8d:

    # ss "I'm not going to talk to you about my relationships."
    ss "No voy a hablar contigo de mis relaciones."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:128
translate spanish breakfastmenu_1422ef63:

    # pc "Why not? What's a big [brother] for, if not for giving advice?"
    pc "¿Por qué no? ¿Para qué sirve un gran [brother], si no es para dar consejos?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:129
translate spanish breakfastmenu_372edb07:

    # ss "In my experience, a big [brother] is only there to be annoying and then abandon you."
    ss "Según mi experiencia, un gran [brother] solo está ahí para molestar y luego abandonarte."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:130
translate spanish breakfastmenu_620cccdd:

    # pc "I didn't abandon you Suzy. I went to college."
    pc "Yo no te abandoné, Suzy. Me fui a la universidad."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:131
translate spanish breakfastmenu_43e8a5ea:

    # ss "Same difference. You could have written or called or something."
    ss "Da lo mismo. Podrías haber escrito o llamado o algo."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:132
translate spanish breakfastmenu_cdfa161d:

    # pc "Well I'm here now. I'm not going to leave again. I'm going to stay and help."
    pc "Bueno, ahora estoy aquí. No voy a marcharme otra vez. Me voy a quedar y ayudar."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:135
translate spanish breakfastmenu_db8d354f:

    # ss "I have no idea. Rumor is that he found another woman and disappeared with her."
    ss "No tengo ni idea. Se rumorea que encontró a otra mujer y desapareció con ella."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:136
translate spanish breakfastmenu_4183655a:

    # pc "Where are you hearing these rumors?"
    pc "¿De dónde sacas esos rumores?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:137
translate spanish breakfastmenu_6f70f528:

    # ss "Just around town."
    ss "Por ahí, en la ciudad."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:138
translate spanish breakfastmenu_adc582ed:

    # pc "Do you think there's any truth to it? Did you ever see him with anybody?"
    pc "¿Crees que hay algo de verdad en ello? ¿Lo viste alguna vez con alguien?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:140
translate spanish breakfastmenu_c058de0d:

    # ss "He was so secretive about everything. He stayed in the basement all the time and barely talked to us in the weeks before he disappeared."
    ss "Era muy reservado con todo. Se pasaba todo el tiempo en el sótano y apenas nos hablaba en las semanas previas a su desaparición."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:141
translate spanish breakfastmenu_0c233c3e:

    # ss "So no, I never saw him with anybody, because I barely saw him at all."
    ss "Así que no, nunca lo vi con nadie, porque apenas lo veía."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:143
translate spanish breakfastmenu_b8c6a91b:

    # ss "I don't know if he left with somebody else, but I wouldn't be surprised. I mean, what else could it be?"
    ss "No sé si se fue con otra persona, pero no me sorprendería. Quiero decir, ¿qué otra cosa podría ser?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:144
translate spanish breakfastmenu_584eeb38:

    # pc "I'm sorry that you had to deal with this all alone."
    pc "Siento que hayas tenido que lidiar con esto tú sola."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:145
translate spanish breakfastmenu_61d6e76f:

    # pc "But I'm here to help now."
    pc "Pero ahora estoy aquí para ayudarte."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:149
translate spanish breakfastmenu_fcfa5eb9:

    # ss "Are you fucking serious?"
    ss "¿Hablas en serio, joder?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:150
translate spanish breakfastmenu_448a6b89:

    # ss "It's my bathroom. Not your bathroom. Not our bathroom. MY bathroom!"
    ss "Es mi baño. No tu baño. No nuestro baño. ¡MI baño!"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:151
translate spanish breakfastmenu_558e1795:

    # ss "If you don't like it, you can just get the fuck out."
    ss "Si no te gusta, puedes largarte."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:152
translate spanish breakfastmenu_e861901c:

    # pc "We're going to have to learn to share."
    pc "Vamos a tener que aprender a compartir."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:153
translate spanish breakfastmenu_5b696ff4:

    # ss "No we're not. You're going to have to learn that it's my space and you can go fuck yourself."
    ss "No, no vamos a tener que hacerlo. Tú vas a tener que aprender que este es mi espacio y que te puedes ir a la mierda."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:154
translate spanish breakfastmenu_2c586b30:

    # pc "What's the use of us being mad at each other all the time?"
    pc "¿De qué sirve que estemos enfadados el uno con el otro todo el tiempo?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:155
translate spanish breakfastmenu_86802cd2:

    # ss "Leave me alone. I don't want to talk to you, I'm just trying to eat breakfast here."
    ss "Déjame en paz. No quiero hablar contigo, solo estoy intentando desayunar."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:156
translate spanish breakfastmenu_15190116:

    # pc "Fine."
    pc "Vale."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:163
translate spanish suzyreconcile_a9b7d881:

    # ss "You talk a big game, but when it comes down to it, you'll run away."
    ss "Hablas mucho, pero a la hora de la verdad, te vas a escapar."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:164
translate spanish suzyreconcile_e9414b02:

    # ss "Just like you ran away to Brazil."
    ss "Igual que te escapaste a Brasil."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:165
translate spanish suzyreconcile_5d857346:

    # pc "I didn't run away. I got a scholarship. It was the best college for my field."
    pc "No me escapé. Conseguí una beca. Era la mejor universidad para mi campo."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:166
translate spanish suzyreconcile_e67211ab:

    # ss "We were just starting to get along. I was actually starting to enjoy having you around. My big [brother]."
    ss "Justo estábamos empezando a llevarnos bien. De hecho, estaba empezando a disfrutar de tenerte cerca. Mi gran [brother]."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:167
translate spanish suzyreconcile_1ddfbed6:

    # ss "Then you just leave and don't even call me, e-mail me, nothing."
    ss "Y entonces te vas y ni siquiera me llamas, ni me envías un correo, nada."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:168
translate spanish suzyreconcile_6e56d9fd:

    # ss "You just leave. It felt like you wanted to get as far away from us as possible."
    ss "Simplemente te vas. Parecía que querías alejarte lo más posible de nosotros."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:169
translate spanish suzyreconcile_65a60962:

    # pc "That wasn't it."
    pc "No fue eso."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:171
translate spanish suzyreconcile_304ad7a9:

    # ss "Don't lie. I can tell when you're lying."
    ss "No mientas. Sé cuándo mientes."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:172
translate spanish suzyreconcile_63428b62:

    # pc "Okay, maybe I did want to get away a bit. But it wasn't about you or Lisa. It was just that I missed my mom and didn't like to see her replaced."
    pc "Vale, quizá sí que quería alejarme un poco. Pero no tenía nada que ver contigo ni con Lisa. Es solo que echaba de menos a mi madre y no me gustaba ver cómo la sustituían."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:173
translate spanish suzyreconcile_238de080:

    # pc "I see now that I was childish then. That you weren't replacing her."
    pc "Ahora me doy cuenta de que entonces fui infantil. De que tú no la estabas sustituyendo."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:174
translate spanish suzyreconcile_e4ed90e5:

    # pc "I'm sorry. I'll do better now."
    pc "Lo siento. Ahora lo haré mejor."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:175
translate spanish suzyreconcile_6e67a0a4:

    # pc "I want us to be friends."
    pc "Quiero que seamos amigos."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:177
translate spanish suzyreconcile_9a7d3359:

    # pc "I care about you Suzy. I really do."
    pc "Me importas, Suzy. De verdad."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:178
translate spanish suzyreconcile_bf55225d:

    # ss "I care about you too, I guess."
    ss "A mí también me importas, supongo."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:179
translate spanish suzyreconcile_02d6656a:

    # pc "So can we put all that junk behind us."
    pc "¿Podemos dejar todo ese lío atrás?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:180
translate spanish suzyreconcile_0ad83f38:

    # ss "Yeah. Let's do that. Let's start over."
    ss "Sí. Hagámoslo. Empecemos de nuevo."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:181
translate spanish suzyreconcile_af3bb346:

    # pc "Great. Love you, [sis]. Glad we had this talk."
    pc "Genial. Te quiero, [sis]. Me alegro de que hayamos tenido esta charla."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:182
translate spanish suzyreconcile_9e6f116f:

    # ss "Do you want to hug or something?"
    ss "¿Quieres un abrazo o algo así?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:183
translate spanish suzyreconcile_67aa3ee7:

    # pc "Yeah, let's do that."
    pc "Sí, hagámoslo."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:186
translate spanish suzyreconcile_c6b79ddd:

    # "We stand up and walk over towards each other. It is awkward at first, but after I wrap my arms around her and pull her close, we both relax."
    "Nos levantamos y caminamos el uno hacia el otro. Al principio es incómodo, pero después de rodearla con mis brazos y acercarla a mí, los dos nos relajamos."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:187
translate spanish suzyreconcile_e43a87e0:

    # "It feels right. I really do care about her and I feel like we can have a real relationship now."
    "Me siento bien. De verdad que me importa y siento que ahora podemos tener una relación de verdad."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:188
translate spanish suzyreconcile_710152a6:

    # ss "I love you too [bro]. I'm glad you're back home."
    ss "Yo también te quiero, [bro]. Me alegro de que hayas vuelto a casa."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:190
translate spanish suzyreconcile_7264edb7:

    # "With that, it's time to go to school, so we say our goodbyes and I head out."
    "Dicho esto, es hora de ir al colegio, así que nos despedimos y me voy."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:194
translate spanish suzynoreconcile_68750ffa:

    # "We sit in silence until eventually Suzy gets up and stomps away upstairs."
    "Nos quedamos sentados en silencio hasta que, al final, Suzy se levanta y sube las escaleras dando pisotones."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:196
translate spanish suzynoreconcile_b9fe82ed:

    # "This hadn't gone as well as I'd hoped. I guess I'll have to try to talk to her some other time."
    "Esto no ha salido tan bien como esperaba. Supongo que tendré que intentar hablar con ella en otra ocasión."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:197
translate spanish suzynoreconcile_db1e9d34:

    # "Right now though, it's time for school, so I clean up my dishes and head out."
    "Pero ahora mismo es hora de ir al colegio, así que recojo los platos y me voy."

translate spanish strings:

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:2
    old "Suzy eats breakfast in the dining room every weekday morning before school."
    new "Suzy desayuna en el comedor todas las mañanas de lunes a viernes antes de ir al colegio."

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:3
    old "You could try to have breakfast with her. Remember to be nice."
    new "Podrías intentar desayunar con ella. Recuerda ser amable."

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:15
    old "How have you been?"
    new "¿Cómo te ha ido?"

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:27
    old "You ever get any weird customers?"
    new "¿Alguna vez has tenido clientes raros?"

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:53
    old "You should be careful messing with people like that."
    new "Deberías tener cuidado al meterte con gente así."

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:64
    old "Yeah, I wouldn't like to see you getting hit either."
    new "Sí, a mí tampoco me gustaría que te pegaran."

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:76
    old "Of course."
    new "Por supuesto."

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:80
    old "You'd probably be good at it; you could put that anger to use."
    new "Probablemente se te daría bien; podrías aprovechar esa ira."

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:86
    old "Do guys ever hit on you too?"
    new "¿Alguna vez te coquetean los chicos también?"

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:96
    old "How much does it pay?"
    new "¿Cuánto te pagan?"

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:107
    old "I think I'd hate it."
    new "Creo que lo odiaría."

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:111
    old "You really think that about me?"
    new "¿De verdad piensas eso de mí?"

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:114
    old "I'm not like that."
    new "Yo no soy así."

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:117
    old "You think that you're good at talking to people?"
    new "¿Crees que se te da bien hablar con la gente?"

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:123
    old "You have a boyfriend?"
    new "¿Tienes novio?"

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:134
    old "Do you know anything about what happened to dad?"
    new "¿Sabes algo de lo que le pasó a papá?"

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:147
    old "You should clean your mess in the bathroom."
    new "Deberías limpiar el desastre que has hecho en el baño."

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:158
    old "Stay quiet and leave her alone."
    new "Cállate y déjala en paz."

